Value: Hawthorn Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a diversified base metals and gold mining and exploration company in Western Australia. It holds an 70% interest in the Trouser Legs project located to the north-east of Kalgoorlie; and 80% interest in the Edjudina project located to the north-east of Kalgoorlie. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
